            "title": "CarMax Non-GAAP EPS of $0.34 beats by $0.13, revenue of $5.95B beats by $220M",
            "description": "<html><body><ul>\n<li>CarMax <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/pr/20471522-carmax-reports-fourth-quarter-and-fiscal-year-2026-results\">press release</a> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/KMX\" title=\"CarMax, Inc.\">KMX</a></span></span></span>): Q4 Non-GAAP EPS of $0.34 <span> beats by $0.13</span>.</li>\n<li>Revenue of $5.95B (-0.8% Y/Y) <span> beats by $220M</span>.</li>\n<li>Combined retail and wholesale unit sales of 303,969, an increase of 0.7%.</li>\n<li>Bought 270,000 vehicles from consumers and dealers, an increase of 0.4%.<ul>\n<li>229,000 vehicles were purchased from consumers, up 2.5%</li>\n<li>41,000 vehicles were purchased through dealers, down 9.5%</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> </li>\n</ul>\n<ul><li>Shares <span>-2%</span> PM.</li></ul>\n<div class=\"signup_widget_placeholder\"></div>\n</body></html>",
